p: Territory of Washington, County of Spokane.}SS. Territory of Washington, Plaintiff vs. S.P. White Defendant }In the District Court of the Territory of Washington and for the Lincoln Judicial District thereof, holding terms at Cheney, Spokane County, in said Territory To the Sheriff of Lincoln County, Greeting: In the name of the United States, You are herebu commanded to summon William Rhodes Wells Williams Jorich Bole to be and appear before the District Court aforesaid at the Court House, in Cheney, in said County, on the day of April A.D. 1885, at o'clock - M., to there give evi- dence in the above entitled cause on the part of said Plaintiff. Witness the Hon. George Turner Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of Washington Territory, and Judge of said Court, and the Seal there- of affixed, this 20 day of April A.D. 1885 Kate Faurbach Clerk. By R.S. Brobuch Deputy
